The paper discusses the addition of references extracted from the arXiv e-prints to the ADS citation database. The paper also mentions the traditional sources of citations, which are typically found in computer science sub-categories such as digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and databases (cs.DB). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
